@page "/privacy-policy"

<div class="container mt-5 pt-5 pb-5 small">
    <h1 class="fw-bold text-uppercase mb-5" style="letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 1.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 text-secondary">
            <p class="mb-4">Last updated: April 2026</p>

            <h6 class="text-dark fw-bold text-uppercase mt-4">1. Information We Collect</h6>
            <p>We collect information you provide directly to us: name, email address, shipping address, and payment information during checkout.</p>

            <h6 class="text-dark fw-bold text-uppercase mt-4">2. Compliance (GDPR & CCPA)</h6>
            <p>For EU residents, we process data under GDPR guidelines. For US residents (specifically California), we comply with CCPA regarding your right to access or delete personal data.</p>

            <h6 class="text-dark fw-bold text-uppercase mt-4">3. Data Security</h6>
            <p>We implement industry-standard encryption (SSL) to protect your data during transmission and storage.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>